WEBVTT

01:37.060 --> 01:40.910
[The Best Thing]

01:41.450 --> 01:48.690
[Episode 20: Paeonia lactiflora]
[Bitter, sour, dispels cold, nourishes blood and regulates menstruation, restrains yin and stops sweating, softens the liver and alleviates pain, pacifies the liver yang]

01:52.200 --> 01:54.680
What's up? Is something wrong?

01:58.390 --> 01:59.560
No, nothing.

02:00.630 --> 02:02.230
I just wanted to tell you that

02:03.950 --> 02:04.960
I missed you.

02:12.790 --> 02:14.200
Thank you for telling me.

02:20.840 --> 02:22.079
I missed you too.

02:44.010 --> 02:44.660
Bye-bye.

02:55.670 --> 02:57.200
Dr. He. Waiting for your girlfriend again?

02:57.220 --> 02:58.180
Yes, indeed.

03:01.140 --> 03:02.310
Here's your spicy hot pot.

03:14.490 --> 03:16.380
You already gave me your door code.

03:16.410 --> 03:17.850
Why did you still come down to meet me?

03:17.990 --> 03:19.270
Didn't you say you missed me?

03:19.290 --> 03:20.730
So I came down early to meet you.

03:20.760 --> 03:21.520
So nice of you.

03:22.550 --> 03:23.760
Dinner's ready. Let's go.

03:24.000 --> 03:25.000
What are we having today?

03:25.470 --> 03:26.430
We're having...

03:26.430 --> 03:27.190
Guess.

03:29.020 --> 03:29.810
Bamboo shoots?

03:30.190 --> 03:30.910
You want bamboo shoots?

03:31.440 --> 03:31.960
Okay.

03:32.110 --> 03:33.240
I'll make another dish for you then.

04:10.960 --> 04:12.240
You're extra supportive of my cooking today.

04:15.820 --> 04:17.029
Got a good appetite?

04:25.540 --> 04:26.650
Today,

04:26.820 --> 04:28.290
I accomplished something big.

04:30.570 --> 04:31.720
Yan Heng checked out.

04:34.270 --> 04:35.390
I always thought

04:35.740 --> 04:37.810
I'd have some kind of argument with him when the time came.

04:38.590 --> 04:40.480
But when it really happened, I was surprisingly calm.

04:41.350 --> 04:42.270
Because...

04:44.070 --> 04:45.550
I've completely moved on.

04:55.310 --> 04:56.400
That indeed

04:56.630 --> 04:58.159
is a big accomplishment.

05:08.960 --> 05:09.880
He Suye.

05:12.510 --> 05:14.830
Thank you for never letting go of my hand.

05:17.720 --> 05:18.830
What are you thanking me for?

05:20.050 --> 05:21.850
Didn't I also get myself a girlfriend?

05:27.220 --> 05:28.380
Alright, let's eat.

05:29.390 --> 05:30.000
Let's eat.

05:35.120 --> 05:35.720
Oh, right.

05:35.880 --> 05:37.880
I need to make a run home after dinner.

05:38.190 --> 05:40.159
My parents have been worried about me because of this.

05:40.159 --> 05:41.600
I need to go home and tell them.

05:42.720 --> 05:43.390
Sure.

05:44.270 --> 05:44.830
Then eat more.

05:44.830 --> 05:45.740
Don't get hungry later.

05:48.010 --> 05:48.690
Is it not good?

05:49.430 --> 05:50.190
It's really good.

05:50.260 --> 05:51.060
Then eat more.

05:51.390 --> 05:52.630
I want some more soup.

05:54.909 --> 05:57.740
You shouldn't eat rice soaked in soup like this. It's bad for your stomach.

06:22.420 --> 06:23.590
That's pretty good.

06:24.670 --> 06:25.670
What kind of person Yan is

06:25.690 --> 06:26.940
is another matter.

06:27.850 --> 06:30.000
Just think of this as a part of your life journey.

06:30.690 --> 06:32.540
Walking gracefully to the end

06:33.230 --> 06:34.480
should be considered a good thing, right?

06:37.430 --> 06:38.960
Did he make you cry?

06:39.640 --> 06:42.440
No. I'm completely fine. Don't worry.

06:49.270 --> 06:50.590
Have you told He about this?

06:52.270 --> 06:53.260
I have.

06:54.730 --> 06:56.060
As you should.

06:56.530 --> 06:57.580
Otherwise, he might be worried.

07:04.040 --> 07:06.310
You should invite He over for dinner,

07:06.840 --> 07:08.620
so that we can formally meet.

07:09.560 --> 07:11.640
Last time he came to our house, it was a complete mess.

07:11.660 --> 07:12.610
We don't want him to think that

07:13.050 --> 07:14.350
our family is not good.

07:17.970 --> 07:19.620
Okay, no problem.

07:20.060 --> 07:20.900
Well,

07:21.200 --> 07:22.440
I'll talk to him about it later.

07:22.710 --> 07:23.260
Alright.

07:38.170 --> 07:39.320
Are you not coming to see me later?

07:42.720 --> 07:45.230
No. I'm going to spend more time with my parents.

07:50.350 --> 07:50.990
By the way,

07:51.130 --> 07:53.500
my parents are asking if you're free this weekend.

07:53.530 --> 07:54.600
They want to invite you over for dinner.

07:56.440 --> 07:57.120
This weekend?

07:57.500 --> 07:58.150
Sure.

07:58.770 --> 08:00.060
Okay, okay.

08:02.040 --> 08:02.730
Ms. Shen.

08:02.920 --> 08:05.310
I remember you haven't taken Chinese medicine for a while.

08:05.340 --> 08:06.990
Why don't you ask Dr. He to check your pulse again

08:07.010 --> 08:08.000
and prescribe some Chinese medicine for you?

08:08.170 --> 08:09.760
Your body still needs conditioning.

08:09.790 --> 08:11.390
I've been doing pretty well lately.

08:11.430 --> 08:12.550
I have a good appetite.

08:12.580 --> 08:13.580
I don't want to take Chinese medicine anymore.

08:13.600 --> 08:14.880
Why not?

08:16.150 --> 08:18.310
Chinese medicine is for long-term health maintenance.

08:20.080 --> 08:20.690
Besides,

08:20.710 --> 08:22.070
who has such easy access to Chinese medicine as you do?

08:22.290 --> 08:23.630
You can just have a date with your boyfriend,

08:23.700 --> 08:25.060
get your pulse checked, and get the medicine prescribed.

08:25.220 --> 08:26.290
And you still don't want to take it?

08:26.310 --> 08:27.500
It's too bitter.

08:28.280 --> 08:29.030
Get up.

08:29.110 --> 08:30.560
-Come downstairs and take a walk with us.
-What?

08:30.580 --> 08:31.970
I'm not going. I just got off work.

08:32.000 --> 08:32.799
I want to rest.

08:33.230 --> 08:34.400
Why are you so lazy?

08:34.419 --> 08:35.260
You just had dinner.

08:35.289 --> 08:37.090
Staying cooped up here isn't good for digestion.

08:37.960 --> 08:39.440
Didn't Dr. He tell you that?

08:40.510 --> 08:41.320
No.

08:42.440 --> 08:44.390
Get up.

08:44.600 --> 08:46.170
Go to your room and put on a coat.

08:46.200 --> 08:46.840
It's cold outside.

08:46.870 --> 08:48.270
Okay.

08:49.850 --> 08:50.850
Tell me quickly that

08:50.880 --> 08:53.470
lying down right after eating doesn't affect digestion.

08:55.560 --> 08:56.960
I don't want to go downstairs for a walk.

09:01.270 --> 09:02.820
Doctors can't lie.

09:25.700 --> 09:26.220
Here you go.

09:26.240 --> 09:27.000
Thank you.

09:27.110 --> 09:28.110
The food is here.

09:28.130 --> 09:28.980
I want that fried cake.

09:29.000 --> 09:30.720
That... Fried cake.

09:30.750 --> 09:32.430
Aren't you two taking a walk to aid digestion after dinner?

09:32.430 --> 09:33.550
Why are you eating again?

09:33.960 --> 09:35.050
It's after-dinner dessert.

09:35.390 --> 09:36.670
We got hungry from walking. Got a problem?

09:37.490 --> 09:38.050
Eat up.

09:39.490 --> 09:41.450
My university is organizing a hike this weekend.

09:41.810 --> 09:42.810
Let's go together.

09:43.070 --> 09:44.270
Those women in our research team...

09:44.270 --> 09:45.290
Mrs. Shen. Mr. Shen.

09:46.120 --> 09:46.750
Good evening.

09:47.140 --> 09:47.900
Good evening.

09:48.350 --> 09:49.030
What a coincidence.

09:50.220 --> 09:51.260
Why are you here?

09:52.630 --> 09:55.170
Well, Xifan told me that you two wanted to see me,

09:55.390 --> 09:56.910
so I quickly got ready and came down.

10:01.690 --> 10:02.530
I...

10:04.270 --> 10:05.360
Right.

10:05.360 --> 10:06.510
Yes. We wanted to meet you.

10:06.510 --> 10:06.910
Well.

10:07.730 --> 10:09.190
I've been telling Xifan

10:09.220 --> 10:10.620
to ask you over for dinner.

10:10.640 --> 10:12.930
We should meet you formally, right?

10:13.100 --> 10:14.410
I must have misunderstood.

10:14.690 --> 10:15.650
But it's convenient anyway.

10:15.890 --> 10:17.260
We live in the same neighborhood, right?

10:17.460 --> 10:18.580
Xifan can give me a call anytime,

10:18.620 --> 10:19.380
and I'll come right over.

10:19.700 --> 10:20.620
-Yes.
-Right.

10:20.640 --> 10:21.600
We've talked about it several times already.

10:21.600 --> 10:22.440
Come anytime.

10:22.720 --> 10:22.960
Okay.

10:22.960 --> 10:24.360
Mr. Shen's cooking is really delicious.

10:24.360 --> 10:25.360
You're flattering me.

10:25.850 --> 10:28.260
When I have a chance, I'll learn from you, Mr. Shen.

10:28.280 --> 10:29.160
I love cooking too.

10:29.520 --> 10:30.560
How's your cooking?

10:31.150 --> 10:31.630
It's okay.

10:32.330 --> 10:33.410
That's great.

10:33.440 --> 10:34.270
From now on, Ms. Shen

10:34.270 --> 10:35.360
won't have to worry about her meals anymore.

10:35.360 --> 10:36.080
Mom.

10:36.390 --> 10:37.200
Dad.

10:40.480 --> 10:41.750
After having my cooking tonight,

10:41.750 --> 10:43.240
why did you sit down again?

10:43.600 --> 10:45.120
Didn't we agree we'd take a walk to digest?

10:45.120 --> 10:45.840
Let's go, let's go.

10:45.840 --> 10:46.720
We're still continuing that walk?

10:47.080 --> 10:49.050
We two need to walk more. We ate too much tonight.

10:49.480 --> 10:50.410
Let's go, let's go.

10:50.440 --> 10:52.120
But I haven't eaten... This yet.

10:52.270 --> 10:52.820
Well,

10:53.180 --> 10:54.570
you guys,

10:54.600 --> 10:55.930
order more yourselves, okay?

10:55.950 --> 10:56.910
-Order yourselves.
-Okay.

10:56.930 --> 10:58.960
See you at home another day.

10:59.030 --> 11:00.390
Let's set a formal date for that meal.

11:00.390 --> 11:01.030
Okay, no problem.

11:01.180 --> 11:02.180
Goodbye. Goodbye.

11:02.200 --> 11:04.080
W-We didn't mean to chase you two away.

11:10.780 --> 11:11.810
I think

11:12.890 --> 11:14.440
your parents like me quite a lot.

11:17.610 --> 11:19.850
You showed up suddenly on purpose, didn't you?

11:21.050 --> 11:21.650
No, I didn't.

11:23.620 --> 11:26.100
Didn't you tell me you were taking a walk with your parents?

11:26.700 --> 11:28.150
Wasn't that specifically to call me over?

11:28.630 --> 11:29.840
I did no such thing.

11:30.470 --> 11:31.310
Isn't that so?

11:32.900 --> 11:33.730
He Suye.

11:34.070 --> 11:34.860
I've discovered

11:34.880 --> 11:36.810
you can be quite shameless sometimes.

11:38.750 --> 11:39.720
It's alright, I guess.

11:45.920 --> 11:47.430
What do you want to eat? I'll order it for you.

11:48.070 --> 11:48.830
You're annoying.

11:54.240 --> 11:55.190
Here.

12:00.540 --> 12:01.270
It's iced.

12:01.930 --> 12:03.180
Without ice. Without ice.

12:03.830 --> 12:05.040
What? Are you going through a rebellious phase?

12:05.230 --> 12:06.460
No.

12:06.480 --> 12:08.800
It's just I suddenly realized yesterday that I don't have to take Chinese medicine anymore.

12:08.830 --> 12:10.960
So I can have some cold drinks now.

12:12.060 --> 12:13.870
You're not afraid of being caught, huh?

12:14.950 --> 12:16.740
If I get caught, I'll just deny it.

12:17.320 --> 12:20.210
Besides, he has to take care of me no matter what.

12:21.510 --> 12:22.360
Nice.

12:23.310 --> 12:24.920
Dr. He doesn't want you to have cold drinks

12:24.940 --> 12:26.020
for your own good.

12:26.760 --> 12:29.060
So you're not letting her have this drink or what?

12:30.160 --> 12:30.680
Go ahead.

12:34.730 --> 12:35.510
Xifan.

12:35.980 --> 12:37.480
Now that you're with Dr. He,

12:37.480 --> 12:38.720
when can we have dinner with him

12:38.720 --> 12:39.910
and let him meet your dearest friends?

12:41.040 --> 12:41.800
How about this weekend?

12:42.850 --> 12:44.850
He works at the clinic on Saturdays.

12:44.880 --> 12:46.050
He doesn't work on Sundays.

12:46.080 --> 12:47.140
We're available this Sunday.

12:48.430 --> 12:49.430
Okay. I'll ask him.

12:52.240 --> 12:54.740
What do you usually do on your dates?

12:55.820 --> 12:56.700
I go to his place,

12:56.720 --> 12:58.410
and he cooks or makes medicated diet for me.

12:59.360 --> 13:00.570
So simple?

13:02.230 --> 13:02.990
Alright then.

13:03.200 --> 13:05.560
I'll take care of all the fun stuff.

13:05.590 --> 13:06.990
You just need to be there.

13:07.020 --> 13:07.770
Thank you, Sis.

13:11.520 --> 13:13.090
My girlfriend is so cool.

13:28.820 --> 13:29.870
The scenery is pretty nice, isn't it?

13:31.710 --> 13:32.470
Xifan.

13:33.190 --> 13:33.870
Coming.

13:37.480 --> 13:39.510
It's really comfortable to take a walk here.

13:40.100 --> 13:41.530
And it's not cold at all.

13:42.060 --> 13:43.870
We've just passed the Awakening of Insects in the solar terms,

13:43.890 --> 13:45.930
which marks the time when spring thunder awakens the hibernating insects

13:45.960 --> 13:47.280
and everything comes back to life.

13:47.570 --> 13:48.540
As for people,

13:48.570 --> 13:50.050
we should also be like those hibernating insects,

13:50.080 --> 13:51.050
coming out to exercise a bit.

13:53.370 --> 13:54.720
He's always like this.

13:55.760 --> 13:56.870
Am I wrong?

13:56.870 --> 13:58.300
Isn't the place I picked really nice?

13:58.330 --> 13:59.570
The atmosphere here is great, isn't it?

13:59.610 --> 14:01.180
I really like it here.

14:03.150 --> 14:04.120
Well...

14:04.430 --> 14:05.510
We forgot to bring drinks, right?

14:05.510 --> 14:06.480
I see they're selling drinks over there.

14:06.480 --> 14:07.360
I'll go buy some.

14:09.320 --> 14:10.770
Comrade, I'll leave them in your care.

14:12.040 --> 14:12.830
Good luck.

14:13.740 --> 14:14.580
Come back soon.

14:16.630 --> 14:17.420
Dr. He.

14:17.650 --> 14:19.340
Could you take a couple of nice photos for us?

14:19.370 --> 14:20.130
With my phone.

14:20.640 --> 14:21.850
You want me to take photos for you?

14:23.920 --> 14:24.490
Okay.

14:24.790 --> 14:25.290
Let's go.

14:25.700 --> 14:26.270
Is it heavy?

14:26.290 --> 14:26.970
It's all right.

14:27.570 --> 14:28.290
Over there, over there.

14:28.320 --> 14:28.720
Let's go.

14:28.740 --> 14:29.460
Be careful.

14:39.910 --> 14:42.630
Dr. He, please don't feel any pressure.

14:42.630 --> 14:43.270
If you really don't know how,

14:43.270 --> 14:44.910
just keep pressing the button over and over.

14:45.650 --> 14:46.910
Taking photos is such a simple task.

14:46.910 --> 14:48.150
How could I feel pressured?

14:48.620 --> 14:50.120
Just a moment, let me adjust the settings.

14:50.310 --> 14:52.460
I need to adjust the white balance, brightness, and such.

14:52.480 --> 14:54.170
He even knows about settings?

14:54.490 --> 14:55.400
I have no idea.

14:55.680 --> 14:56.440
Done.

14:56.560 --> 14:57.920
Come on, look here.

15:00.080 --> 15:00.890
So pretty.

15:01.270 --> 15:02.240
One more.

15:02.240 --> 15:03.440
Three, two, one.

15:04.970 --> 15:05.720
Xiangya.

15:06.100 --> 15:08.620
His photos on social media are really ugly.

15:09.260 --> 15:10.140
Smile bigger.

15:10.170 --> 15:11.840
With such beautiful models,

15:12.560 --> 15:14.200
it would be hard for him to take ugly photos of us, okay?

15:14.430 --> 15:15.560
You two, look at each other.

15:16.210 --> 15:17.850
Three, two, one.

15:18.200 --> 15:19.170
Look at me, look at me.

15:19.850 --> 15:20.940
Something's not right.

15:21.490 --> 15:24.260
Why do I feel he's getting further and further away from us?

15:26.070 --> 15:27.790
Three, two, one.

15:30.580 --> 15:31.820
I think we should call him.

15:32.470 --> 15:33.840
Dr. He, don't go any further.

15:33.840 --> 15:34.510
Come back for a moment.

15:43.900 --> 15:44.290
Look.

15:44.320 --> 15:44.960
Take a look.

15:45.280 --> 15:46.010
How are they?

15:46.630 --> 15:47.580
Aren't they absolutely pretty?

16:01.940 --> 16:02.920
Aren't they gorgeous?

16:03.050 --> 16:04.810
We asked you to take close-ups.

16:05.860 --> 16:06.860
There are close-ups.

16:07.490 --> 16:08.680
Look at the first few ones.

16:11.000 --> 16:11.600
This one.

16:12.460 --> 16:13.250
Do you see it?

16:14.340 --> 16:15.410
Both your heads are big in this one.

16:16.670 --> 16:17.350
Aren't they?

16:18.790 --> 16:20.320
Are our heads really that big?

16:20.590 --> 16:22.120
Are our legs really that short?

16:22.140 --> 16:23.450
Are we really that fat?

16:25.160 --> 16:25.850
But...

16:26.850 --> 16:28.180
But you do look like this

16:28.520 --> 16:29.400
to me normally.

16:29.430 --> 16:30.240
What?

16:35.240 --> 16:36.630
Is there... Is there any problem?

16:39.370 --> 16:40.210
Don't they look good?

16:42.550 --> 16:44.150
Lin Yishen!

16:44.940 --> 16:45.940
Pretty. Really pretty.

16:45.960 --> 16:46.800
Stand closer.

16:46.870 --> 16:48.080
Right, closer.

16:48.430 --> 16:49.830
Yes, that's right, that's right.

16:49.860 --> 16:51.340
Hug, hug.

16:51.360 --> 16:51.970
Hug.

16:53.240 --> 16:54.360
Got it, got it.

16:54.380 --> 16:55.660
We've got some great shots.

16:56.090 --> 16:57.090
The last few ones.

16:57.750 --> 16:58.660
Show your teeth.

16:59.120 --> 17:00.600
Yes, show your teeth.

17:00.900 --> 17:01.440
Right, right.

17:01.440 --> 17:02.360
"Got some great shots"?

17:03.240 --> 17:04.270
I can take great shots too.

17:05.819 --> 17:06.170
What's...

17:07.109 --> 17:07.960
What's so great about it?

17:07.960 --> 17:08.740
The last two.

17:08.760 --> 17:09.280
Okay.

17:09.400 --> 17:10.720
X-rays count as shots too, you know.

17:11.339 --> 17:11.900
Check them.

17:12.349 --> 17:14.240
Wow, these are so pretty.

17:14.550 --> 17:15.440
How are they? Are you satisfied?

17:16.230 --> 17:17.960
They're really well taken.

17:18.810 --> 17:19.440
Comrade.

17:19.470 --> 17:20.640
Let's go, time to go to the next location.

17:27.880 --> 17:28.680
Can you hold this for me?

17:28.680 --> 17:30.000
I'll go to the next location first.

17:30.000 --> 17:30.420
Go ahead.

17:30.440 --> 17:31.040
I'm going.

17:31.070 --> 17:31.920
Can you hold this for me too?

17:32.810 --> 17:33.330
Let's go.

17:36.310 --> 17:36.590
Let's go.

17:36.610 --> 17:37.060
Wait.

17:38.860 --> 17:40.620
When you say comrade, you mean these things?

17:41.000 --> 17:42.680
Sacrificing me to help you succeed?

17:43.870 --> 17:44.890
Buddy, you should know that

17:44.920 --> 17:47.070
in the past, all these things were on me.

17:47.160 --> 17:48.590
I used to act as a coat rack

17:48.590 --> 17:50.200
while also taking photos for them.

17:50.220 --> 17:51.620
Now, I finally have you

17:51.640 --> 17:53.090
to help me share the burden.

17:53.120 --> 17:54.670
Of course, you should know that

17:54.690 --> 17:56.120
in the days to come,

17:56.260 --> 17:59.030
there will be many more moments for us to fight together.

18:01.790 --> 18:03.110
That actually makes sense.

18:04.790 --> 18:05.930
It was my fault for not giving it much thought.

18:06.280 --> 18:08.210
I originally thought we were just coming out for a walk today

18:08.240 --> 18:09.030
to enjoy the scenery.

18:09.170 --> 18:09.970
Buddy.

18:10.640 --> 18:12.770
Your awareness still needs improvement.

18:13.430 --> 18:15.120
When you go out with your girlfriend,

18:15.140 --> 18:16.420
isn't the most beautiful scenery

18:16.450 --> 18:18.080
your own girlfriend?

18:20.770 --> 18:21.420
I'm off.

18:26.380 --> 18:27.220
Wait a moment.

18:27.990 --> 18:29.400
Can't you help me carry some of these?

18:29.720 --> 18:30.550
Come on, hurry up.

18:30.550 --> 18:31.830
They'll get impatient if we keep them waiting.

18:35.330 --> 18:36.090
Hold on.

18:45.110 --> 18:46.110
Look over there.

18:46.510 --> 18:47.510
Look at the camera.

18:50.160 --> 18:50.970
This is a video,

18:51.000 --> 18:51.650
not a photo.

18:52.750 --> 18:54.430
Videos look more natural.

18:54.450 --> 18:55.350
You can take a screenshot of

18:55.350 --> 18:56.990
the frame you like. It looks much better than a photo.

18:57.520 --> 18:58.200
I didn't know we could do that.

18:58.970 --> 18:59.510
Come on.

19:06.680 --> 19:08.640
Why did you suddenly kiss me?

19:09.330 --> 19:11.040
Didn't you say this way of taking photos is more natural?

19:12.470 --> 19:14.190
You're a quick learner when it comes to this, aren't you?

19:14.620 --> 19:16.410
Of course. Just look at who taught me.

19:19.670 --> 19:20.980
Today,

19:21.480 --> 19:22.440
are you happy?

19:24.100 --> 19:24.900
Today,

19:25.090 --> 19:26.330
I guess I'm pretty happy.

19:26.840 --> 19:29.160
I just didn't expect my girlfriend to complain

19:29.180 --> 19:30.090
about my photography skills.

19:30.550 --> 19:32.840
I didn't complain about your photography skills.

19:32.920 --> 19:34.000
Let me comfort you then.

19:36.010 --> 19:36.860
Alright.

19:36.890 --> 19:38.090
How could I really be angry?

19:40.930 --> 19:42.280
Actually, I'm quite happy today.

19:42.730 --> 19:43.860
The last time I saw them

19:43.890 --> 19:45.330
was during the medicated diet project.

19:46.110 --> 19:47.590
We were all in work mode then.

19:47.910 --> 19:49.830
I didn't expect them to be like this in private.

19:51.590 --> 19:52.590
Don't laugh. Don't laugh.

19:52.590 --> 19:53.270
Besides,

19:53.680 --> 19:54.720
I also learned

19:54.720 --> 19:55.830
a new way of taking photos from my girlfriend.

19:56.190 --> 19:57.150
How could I not be happy?

20:00.660 --> 20:03.590
They are my best friends.

20:04.850 --> 20:06.850
Seeing you get along well with them,

20:07.470 --> 20:09.320
it actually makes me really happy.

22:02.960 --> 22:05.040
Senior Lin set up a group chat for us.

22:05.570 --> 22:06.930
He posted today's photos there.

22:13.450 --> 22:14.140
They're pretty, aren't they?

22:14.340 --> 22:16.630
So that's how you take this kind of photo.

22:21.240 --> 22:22.170
Let me try.

22:23.310 --> 22:25.030
You're quite diligent, aren't you?

22:25.060 --> 22:26.490
Come on, there's more to see.

22:26.600 --> 22:28.950
I'm just worried you'll complain about it again.

22:28.970 --> 22:29.860
I didn't complain about it.

22:29.890 --> 22:31.000
You didn't?

22:34.240 --> 22:35.870
Why don't you pick a photo and send it to Grandpa?

22:36.200 --> 22:38.260
He's so envious knowing we're together.

22:38.400 --> 22:39.460
How about you cheer him up a bit?

22:41.560 --> 22:42.670
What about this one?

22:44.210 --> 22:45.500
Okay, this one will do.

22:45.750 --> 22:46.880
I'll send it to you then.

22:52.920 --> 22:55.600
Come to think of it, it's already been a year since we first met.

22:56.420 --> 22:59.150
The cherry blossoms were blooming when we first met.

23:00.040 --> 23:02.130
At that time, I was seeing you for my insomnia.

23:02.470 --> 23:03.330
That's right.

23:03.550 --> 23:04.760
I put in so much effort to pursue you.

23:05.090 --> 23:06.460
I worked hard too, okay?

23:06.480 --> 23:07.650
This is what we call mutual effort.

23:11.870 --> 23:12.900
There's even a video.

23:13.000 --> 23:13.750
Let me show you.

23:13.750 --> 23:14.440
What video?

23:14.910 --> 23:16.530
The video we recorded there.

23:22.790 --> 23:23.470
This is a video.

23:23.490 --> 23:24.580
Look. Look at you.

23:27.680 --> 23:29.000
This video is pretty good too.

23:29.400 --> 23:30.110
Send it to me.

23:30.110 --> 23:31.310
I'll take a screenshot and send it to Grandpa.

23:31.440 --> 23:31.960
Sure.

23:32.870 --> 23:35.190
Three, two, one.

23:35.280 --> 23:35.850
Screenshot.

23:37.270 --> 23:37.790
How is it?

23:38.640 --> 23:39.270
This one's not bad.

23:39.270 --> 23:40.140
You winked like this.

23:40.470 --> 23:41.600
Right?

23:42.660 --> 23:44.530
Okay, I'll go with this one then.

23:44.550 --> 23:45.550
Okay. Let me crop it a bit.

23:46.910 --> 23:49.150
Wow, so sweet.

23:52.590 --> 23:53.350
Don't you think

23:53.350 --> 23:55.110
they look a bit like a married couple?

23:55.110 --> 23:55.720
Are you serious?

23:56.820 --> 23:58.650
My daughter is better looking than him, okay?

23:58.990 --> 24:01.340
But Dr. He is so handsome.

24:01.560 --> 24:03.480
Remember how he caused a stir

24:03.510 --> 24:04.160
in the residents' group chat back then?

24:04.160 --> 24:05.000
I remember.

24:06.130 --> 24:06.880
The vibe of this photo is really great.

24:06.880 --> 24:07.720
The vibe is especially good.

24:07.720 --> 24:08.830
Xiangya and Senior Lin took this.

24:08.930 --> 24:09.500
Right?

24:09.620 --> 24:10.210
It's really pretty.

24:10.790 --> 24:11.760
This is good. It's secretly photographed.

24:12.480 --> 24:14.030
Both the people and the scenery are beautiful.

24:14.670 --> 24:15.540
Happy.

24:15.560 --> 24:16.610
I'm envious.

24:17.210 --> 24:19.250
One day, can we also...

24:20.580 --> 24:21.650
You're so ugly,

24:22.020 --> 24:23.280
how could you achieve that effect?

24:23.310 --> 24:25.270
We'll just take a photo together as a memento.

24:25.270 --> 24:26.790
It's not like we're doing it for some other purpose.

24:26.790 --> 24:27.270
Look how beautiful the scenery is.

24:27.270 --> 24:28.720
I'll have to properly edit your photos then.

24:28.720 --> 24:29.440
That's right.

25:24.880 --> 25:27.750
This is like the iron tree blooming,

25:27.870 --> 25:29.550
and spring coming upon a withered tree.

25:33.520 --> 25:34.560
I'm a little shy.

25:43.540 --> 25:44.540
That's wonderful.

25:46.710 --> 25:49.470
You two are truly a couple destined to be together.

25:51.360 --> 25:53.270
It's wonderful, really wonderful.

25:57.640 --> 25:58.440
Oh, by the way,

25:59.200 --> 25:59.920
Shen,

26:00.790 --> 26:02.740
I'm checking out the day after tomorrow.

26:03.160 --> 26:04.640
Ah, what's the matter?

26:06.050 --> 26:08.290
I'm going back to

26:08.470 --> 26:09.800
live with my kids.

26:10.060 --> 26:12.350
This way, I can hang out with my grandchildren every day.

26:13.790 --> 26:15.270
Why so sudden?

26:16.710 --> 26:18.840
Originally, due to the side effects of radiotherapy,

26:18.870 --> 26:20.360
I was worried that I'd trouble them

26:20.440 --> 26:21.920
and they'd be concerned.

26:22.010 --> 26:24.050
So I thought I'd come back to China for a trip.

26:25.050 --> 26:26.490
But during this time,

26:26.520 --> 26:28.690
Dr. He has treated me very well.

26:29.160 --> 26:30.560
I rarely cough now,

26:31.160 --> 26:34.030
and my mental state has improved a lot.

26:36.180 --> 26:37.580
Also, seeing you like this

26:38.240 --> 26:40.550
makes me want to see my kids too.

26:43.640 --> 26:44.230
Xifan.

26:46.950 --> 26:48.600
During this time, really,

26:49.200 --> 26:51.200
thank you so much for your care.

26:51.790 --> 26:52.800
Not at all.

26:52.830 --> 26:55.350
I'm actually really happy to chat with you.

26:59.620 --> 27:01.380
When are you going to Switzerland?

27:03.270 --> 27:04.310
In October, I guess.

27:05.320 --> 27:06.430
October...

27:10.350 --> 27:13.400
If my health condition allows,

27:14.430 --> 27:15.920
I'll go to Switzerland to visit you.

27:16.000 --> 27:16.830
Really?

27:17.400 --> 27:18.170
That'll be great.

27:18.200 --> 27:20.050
I'll send you my location when I get to Switzerland then.

27:20.310 --> 27:20.830
Okay.

27:23.070 --> 27:24.120
There's one more thing.

27:24.150 --> 27:25.670
Could you arrange for me

27:25.700 --> 27:27.810
to see Dr. He one more time?

27:28.700 --> 27:29.870
Preferably

27:29.890 --> 27:31.990
at a time when you can be there too.

27:32.960 --> 27:34.040
Is that okay?

27:37.030 --> 27:37.750
No problem.

27:43.900 --> 27:44.620
Great.

27:56.170 --> 27:58.480
Your lungs and throat have improved a lot now.

27:58.840 --> 27:59.990
You should keep warm in daily life,

28:00.020 --> 28:00.820
and avoid catching cold.

28:01.210 --> 28:03.180
Eat more moisturizing foods,

28:03.210 --> 28:05.040
such as lilies and pears.

28:05.440 --> 28:06.280
Okay.

28:06.310 --> 28:07.360
But most importantly,

28:07.390 --> 28:09.300
you still need to have regular tumor check-ups.

28:10.590 --> 28:11.270
Thank you for your trouble.

28:11.270 --> 28:12.110
Dr. He.

28:12.660 --> 28:15.660
Thank you and Xifan for taking care of me during this time.

28:16.490 --> 28:18.300
I want to give you two

28:18.550 --> 28:19.620
a gift.

28:25.450 --> 28:26.380
Paeonia lactiflora,

28:26.780 --> 28:28.020
also known as "Jiangli" (about to leave).

28:28.670 --> 28:29.990
I'm about to leave,

28:30.270 --> 28:33.400
but I want to leave this affection and blessing with you.

28:33.890 --> 28:36.090
I hope you'll be happy and blessed.

28:36.720 --> 28:37.960
Thank you both.

28:38.830 --> 28:39.630
How's it?

28:39.650 --> 28:40.330
Looks good?

28:41.380 --> 28:43.410
It feels like this wall isn't so empty anymore.

28:45.350 --> 28:47.250
Alright, I'll go wash my hands first.

28:47.280 --> 28:48.480
I'll cook for you in a bit.

29:35.540 --> 29:42.980
♫Love love love love, is right in front of me♫

29:40.760 --> 29:43.280
Dr. He, let me do you a favor.

29:43.660 --> 29:51.350
♫Ooh love, ooh love, I've seen your face♫

29:44.180 --> 29:45.380
Doesn't it look like a ring?

29:47.590 --> 29:48.400
It's yours now.

29:49.620 --> 29:52.920
I lost that thing you gave me at noon.

29:51.910 --> 29:59.170
♫Love love love love, is talking right at me♫

29:54.330 --> 29:56.130
It disappeared right when I got off work.

29:56.680 --> 29:58.570
How about I buy you another one?

29:59.470 --> 30:06.420
♫Loving you, loving you, is the best thing I'll ever do♫

30:16.980 --> 30:17.700
He Suye.

30:19.330 --> 30:20.810
What is this?

30:23.230 --> 30:25.710
This... What is this?

30:26.360 --> 30:29.190
I found it on your tool shelf.

30:30.270 --> 30:31.080
Tell me.

30:34.060 --> 30:34.930
Oh, right.

30:35.440 --> 30:37.650
Isn't this the metal ring from your key chain?

30:39.540 --> 30:40.640
I lost it at the time.

30:40.790 --> 30:42.570
Later, I found it under the sofa,

30:42.710 --> 30:43.750
so I just put it away casually.

30:43.770 --> 30:46.110
Wait a minute, casually?

30:46.170 --> 30:48.650
You first casually put it on the tray by the door.

30:48.680 --> 30:50.550
Now you say you casually put it on the tool rack.

30:50.550 --> 30:52.160
Keeping such a small thing for so long.

30:52.180 --> 30:52.660
Tell me.

30:52.690 --> 30:54.520
Did you like me from the very beginning?

30:56.610 --> 30:57.320
That makes sense.

30:57.750 --> 30:58.440
I've finally found

30:58.440 --> 31:00.070
the reason why I hid it.

31:00.090 --> 31:01.040
So that's it.

31:01.950 --> 31:02.920
You...

31:02.920 --> 31:04.400
It's obvious you were the one who fell for me first,

31:04.400 --> 31:06.000
yet you're claiming I made a move on you first.

31:06.000 --> 31:06.760
Get back here.

31:07.900 --> 31:09.380
Me liking you and you making a move on me

31:09.400 --> 31:10.750
aren't contradictory.

31:11.720 --> 31:13.350
When you gave this to me as a wedding ring

31:13.350 --> 31:14.110
at that time,

31:14.110 --> 31:15.000
weren't you making a move on me?

31:15.000 --> 31:16.400
Who gave it to you as a wedding ring?

31:16.400 --> 31:18.000
I was just helping you out of a tight spot.

31:18.000 --> 31:18.680
So you admit it.

31:19.770 --> 31:20.860
You did give it to me as a gift.

31:21.500 --> 31:22.700
You made a move on me first.

31:25.360 --> 31:27.410
I'm a man in my thirties.

31:28.000 --> 31:29.640
How could I have resisted such a hint?

31:29.830 --> 31:31.310
So as soon as you gave me a hint, I took the bait, didn't I?

31:31.310 --> 31:32.310
No one was giving you a hint, okay?

31:32.310 --> 31:33.170
Alright, stop talking.

31:34.820 --> 31:35.620
As for this thing,

31:36.520 --> 31:38.090
I've always treasured it.

31:38.560 --> 31:39.350
Now,

31:39.620 --> 31:41.590
I'm going to keep it somewhere else.

31:41.940 --> 31:43.640
He Suye, come here.

31:52.670 --> 31:53.430
I...

31:53.700 --> 31:55.450
Made a move on him first?

32:04.370 --> 32:05.570
What are you carrying?

32:06.930 --> 32:08.440
I brought some medicinal herbs from the clinic.

32:08.810 --> 32:09.810
It's currently the change of seasons, right?

32:10.100 --> 32:12.010
I'm planning to make some new medicated diet for you.

32:14.270 --> 32:17.100
Are there any Chinese herbs that can be steeped in water?

32:17.500 --> 32:18.670
I'd like to make tea of it at the hotel.

32:19.450 --> 32:20.170
Licorice root.

32:21.790 --> 32:22.400
That works.

32:22.400 --> 32:24.250
Alright, I'll get you some in a bit.

32:32.850 --> 32:33.480
Licorice root

32:33.750 --> 32:34.800
has a sweet taste and neutral nature.

32:34.830 --> 32:35.870
It clears heat and detoxifies,

32:36.030 --> 32:37.080
tonifies the spleen and boosts qi.

32:37.380 --> 32:39.380
You can take a few slices and steep them in water to drink.

32:39.590 --> 32:41.110
It probably tastes as good as bubble tea.

32:47.900 --> 32:49.750
At 11:45 PM,

32:49.930 --> 32:51.690
he asked, "Still not sleeping?"

32:52.200 --> 32:53.920
Do you think a guy would care

32:53.920 --> 32:56.290
when a woman he's not interested in goes to sleep?

32:56.890 --> 32:58.650
He barely posts on WeChat Moments.

32:58.680 --> 32:59.230
Look.

32:59.250 --> 33:00.940
He posted one about licorice root.

33:01.140 --> 33:03.710
This handsome TCM physician is quite calculating.

33:04.200 --> 33:05.880
He clearly posted it on Moments on purpose

33:05.880 --> 33:07.830
to make you like it, so that he could chat with you.

33:07.830 --> 33:08.590
And what happened?

33:08.610 --> 33:10.890
You're only liking his post from months ago now.

33:13.940 --> 33:14.690
He Suye.

33:15.260 --> 33:17.300
That post on Moments about licorice root from before.

33:17.670 --> 33:18.990
You posted it on purpose, didn't you?

33:22.750 --> 33:23.390
I didn't.

33:24.090 --> 33:25.200
I was having dinner at Grandpa's.

33:25.380 --> 33:26.620
I happened to have some licorice root water,

33:26.650 --> 33:28.210
so I casually posted about it.

33:29.300 --> 33:30.670
Is that so?

33:30.690 --> 33:33.090
But Senior Lin said you did it on purpose.

33:39.070 --> 33:40.550
So you listened to him

33:40.550 --> 33:41.790
and started to make a move on me?

33:44.200 --> 33:44.660
I...

33:45.440 --> 33:46.610
In that case,

33:46.640 --> 33:48.600
we should thank Senior Lin.

33:52.400 --> 33:52.790
I...

33:52.830 --> 33:53.030
Didn't...

33:53.030 --> 33:53.400
Let's go.

33:53.920 --> 33:54.750
When we get home,

33:54.750 --> 33:57.270
let's give him a call to thank him.

33:57.600 --> 33:58.950
Without him, we wouldn't be together.

33:59.440 --> 34:01.370
I... Made a move on you?

34:05.390 --> 34:08.320
[Honganmen Clinic]

34:09.130 --> 34:10.080
Wait for me a moment.

34:10.380 --> 34:11.510
I have a document to sign.

34:11.880 --> 34:12.429
Okay.

34:14.820 --> 34:16.230
The pharmacy closes at 5 PM.

34:16.230 --> 34:16.960
Pharmacy decoction

34:16.980 --> 34:18.889
takes about four hours.

34:19.600 --> 34:20.810
So,

34:20.840 --> 34:23.280
you can come pick it up at around 2 PM.

34:23.580 --> 34:24.190
I'll leave it here.

34:24.429 --> 34:25.320
-Take care.
-Thank you.

34:27.590 --> 34:28.710
Miss Shen.

34:29.150 --> 34:30.780
Our pharmacy closes at 5 PM.

34:31.070 --> 34:31.880
Pharmacy decoction

34:32.389 --> 34:34.090
takes about four hours.

34:34.440 --> 34:35.230
So,

34:35.340 --> 34:38.940
you can come pick it up at around 2 PM.

34:39.380 --> 34:41.810
Miss Shen, I forgot to remind you.

34:41.920 --> 34:43.520
The pharmacy closes at 5 PM.

34:43.630 --> 34:44.360
Pharmacy decoction

34:44.360 --> 34:46.020
takes four hours.

34:46.540 --> 34:47.350
So,

34:47.630 --> 34:49.739
you can come pick it up at around 2 PM.

34:53.920 --> 34:54.610
Let's go.

34:56.440 --> 34:57.210
What's wrong?

34:57.520 --> 34:58.290
He Suye.

34:58.710 --> 34:59.960
Every time a patient collects medicine,

34:59.960 --> 35:02.030
the pharmacy gives them a reminder, right?

35:02.510 --> 35:03.440
Then that time,

35:03.440 --> 35:04.960
why did you specially come out

35:04.960 --> 35:06.360
to remind me?

35:08.640 --> 35:10.810
I always remind my patients.

35:11.290 --> 35:12.020
Really?

35:12.190 --> 35:12.910
Yes.

35:13.040 --> 35:13.730
Really?

35:13.760 --> 35:14.710
Come on, let's go.

35:14.740 --> 35:15.740
Why are you standing here?

35:16.110 --> 35:16.960
Really?

35:17.620 --> 35:18.670
Are you lying to me?

35:24.300 --> 35:24.970
What would you like to eat?

35:26.560 --> 35:28.250
Quail eggs, noodles,

35:28.280 --> 35:29.280
shrimp paste,

35:29.280 --> 35:30.440
fresh tripe, and squid tentacles.

35:30.440 --> 35:31.230
A bit of everything.

35:31.230 --> 35:32.230
And make it two.

35:32.230 --> 35:32.670
Two portions.

35:32.670 --> 35:33.360
And one...

35:33.360 --> 35:34.070
One with spice,

35:34.070 --> 35:35.110
and the other without.

35:35.110 --> 35:36.030
Okay, got it.

35:36.030 --> 35:36.590
Please wait a moment.

35:44.830 --> 35:45.710
Still thinking about it?

35:48.760 --> 35:50.030
Under normal circumstances,

35:50.030 --> 35:51.360
I would remind my patients,

35:51.550 --> 35:53.320
in case Ms. Wu at the pharmacy forgets.

35:53.840 --> 35:55.680
But you left so quickly that day.

35:55.710 --> 35:57.750
I didn't have a chance to remind you before you left.

35:58.130 --> 35:59.130
So I had to

35:59.160 --> 36:00.910
hurry out to remind you.

36:01.110 --> 36:02.030
What if you went there too early

36:02.030 --> 36:03.360
and couldn't get your medicine?

36:08.520 --> 36:09.260
That's not right.

36:10.020 --> 36:12.620
You were wearing a mask when you examined me.

36:12.640 --> 36:14.640
Why did you take it off when you came out?

36:21.990 --> 36:25.320
You don't think I took off my mask on purpose, do you?

36:28.300 --> 36:29.260
Come on.

36:29.670 --> 36:31.070
Doctors in hospitals take off their masks

36:31.070 --> 36:32.150
to get some fresh air too, you know.

36:32.660 --> 36:34.230
I just happened to run into you.

36:34.250 --> 36:35.330
What could I do about it?

36:38.200 --> 36:38.880
Is that so?

36:39.120 --> 36:39.890
What else could it be?

36:44.190 --> 36:45.880
You don't think I took off my mask and came out

36:45.880 --> 36:47.840
to see you out of some ulterior motive, do you?

36:50.140 --> 36:51.350
I think

36:51.370 --> 36:54.120
you had ulterior motives from the first time you saw me.

36:55.980 --> 36:57.940
Who's the one with ulterior motives here?

36:58.590 --> 36:59.800
The first time you saw me,

36:59.800 --> 37:01.510
you looked me up and down from head to toe.

37:01.510 --> 37:02.800
Don't think I didn't notice.

37:07.110 --> 37:08.610
Also, the way you looked at me,

37:09.740 --> 37:10.650
it was like this.

37:11.070 --> 37:12.720
Correction. I didn't look at you like that.

37:13.190 --> 37:14.150
I'm a TCM physician.

37:14.360 --> 37:15.320
I was taking your pulse.

37:15.320 --> 37:16.400
I could tell from your pulse.

37:18.230 --> 37:20.510
Besides, I did remind you

37:20.760 --> 37:22.550
to stay calm during pulse taking.

37:22.580 --> 37:23.390
Did you manage to do that?

37:25.530 --> 37:27.300
Alright, let's not say anything more.

37:27.600 --> 37:28.600
Thank you, Boss.

37:30.480 --> 37:31.480
Chopsticks.

37:31.500 --> 37:32.140
Here.

37:32.170 --> 37:32.740
Okay.

37:34.700 --> 37:35.490
Not bad.

37:41.490 --> 37:43.190
Don't eat the spicy one. Eat the one with broth.

37:51.970 --> 37:54.260
He Suye, I need to clarify something.

37:54.360 --> 37:55.800
The first time I saw you,

37:55.800 --> 37:57.280
I didn't have any feelings for you.

37:57.280 --> 37:59.230
Besides, at that time, Yan Heng and I hadn't...

38:03.220 --> 38:04.090
In short,

38:04.360 --> 38:06.110
I had no feelings for you at that time.

38:06.340 --> 38:09.700
I'm a very loyal person. Don't worry.

38:11.510 --> 38:12.400
Okay.

38:13.440 --> 38:14.520
I didn't say you weren't loyal.

38:14.550 --> 38:15.470
I was just joking.

38:17.020 --> 38:17.800
Alright, we're done eating.

38:17.800 --> 38:18.990
Let's go home now that we're full.

38:19.940 --> 38:20.500
Let's go.

38:21.440 --> 38:22.080
Boss,

38:22.240 --> 38:22.930
we're leaving.

38:23.270 --> 38:23.980
Okay.

38:24.000 --> 38:24.640
Goodbye.

38:46.630 --> 38:47.920
I've finished washing the dishes.

38:48.480 --> 38:49.560
Let me wipe this.

38:49.710 --> 38:50.320
I'll do it.

38:50.320 --> 38:51.550
It's okay. Go play with your phone for a bit.

38:52.650 --> 38:53.890
Go wash your hands,

38:53.910 --> 38:55.350
and apply some hand cream.

38:57.360 --> 38:58.280
What are you up to?

38:58.630 --> 38:59.320
Go.

38:59.840 --> 39:01.190
Why should I wash my hands?

39:02.220 --> 39:02.860
Just go.

39:11.480 --> 39:12.370
They're clean now.

39:14.220 --> 39:14.990
Feel them.

39:16.750 --> 39:17.970
Feel what?

39:18.200 --> 39:19.150
What do you want to do then?

39:29.200 --> 39:30.110
What's this?

39:59.400 --> 40:00.360
So sudden.

40:09.840 --> 40:10.670
He Suye.

40:12.130 --> 40:14.300
Now that I've got you,

40:15.000 --> 40:18.120
I should take responsibility for you.

40:20.900 --> 40:23.010
That metal ring from before doesn't count.

40:23.810 --> 40:27.170
This time I bought you a real ring.

40:49.270 --> 40:50.540
You put it on the wrong finger.

40:51.590 --> 40:52.670
What are you thinking?

40:52.670 --> 40:54.280
It's too early to put it on that finger, okay?

40:56.470 --> 40:58.360
I thought you were proposing to me.

40:59.110 --> 41:00.060
I got my hopes up for nothing.

41:00.490 --> 41:01.490
No fun.

41:27.420 --> 41:28.350
He Suye.

41:29.470 --> 41:31.590
Even if the ring is on your middle finger,

41:32.430 --> 41:33.150
you

41:33.760 --> 41:35.510
are still mine, Shen Xifan's.

41:36.350 --> 41:38.200
I'll take responsibility for you for the rest of my life.

41:41.520 --> 41:42.300
Are you satisfied now?

41:43.290 --> 41:44.080
I am.

41:54.280 --> 41:55.110
Is it pretty?

41:55.320 --> 41:56.090
Sure it is.

41:57.170 --> 41:59.580
Since I've given you such a beautiful ring,

42:00.290 --> 42:01.850
what reward do you have for me?

42:03.240 --> 42:04.210
What do you want?

42:06.720 --> 42:09.360
How about you go out with me on a trip in a few days when the holiday comes?

42:10.920 --> 42:11.730
Sure.

42:12.770 --> 42:13.500
Wait, no.

42:14.180 --> 42:16.930
It's Qingming Festival in a couple of days.

42:18.210 --> 42:19.290
I need to go visit

42:19.310 --> 42:20.270
my mom's grave.

42:23.720 --> 42:25.420
I'll go early in the morning with my grandpa,

42:25.600 --> 42:26.910
but I'll be back by evening.

42:28.540 --> 42:30.140
Spend some quality time with Professor Yu then.

42:30.790 --> 42:32.870
Let's put this on the tab for now.

42:33.430 --> 42:34.620
Remember to pay me back.
